# Code Push to GitHub Complete

The accumulation of changes from several feature cycles (Sequential Approvals, HOD Projects Flow, and UI Modernization) has been cleaned, organized, and pushed to the `main` branch on GitHub.

## Changes Made

### 1. Workspace Cleanup
- **Discarded Junk**: Removed `backend.zip`, `frontend.zip`, `fix.js`, and `server/scratch/`.
- **Repository Hygiene**: Updated [.gitignore](file:///c:/Apps/Leave%20Tracker/.gitignore) to exclude these patterns in the future.

### 2. Logical Commits
Changes were grouped into three distinct commits to maintain a clean and readable history:

- **[Backend] Database & Workflow Logic**:
  - Updated Prisma schemas for sequential reservation support.
